<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/155868-the-dalai-lama-says-that-it-is-every">The Dalai Lama says that it is every person&#39;s right to seek happiness. But what if seeking this happiness involves harming others in the process? How can this be justified? And how do we distinguish that sort of happiness from the real deal?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
