<div id="review_1958653918" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1958653918" />
    <a title="Farah Cook" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/61751359-farah-cook"><img alt="Farah Cook" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1514810059p2/61751359.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1958653918?book_show_action=true">Mar 31, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Farah Cook" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Farah Cook" href="/user/show/61751359-farah-cook">Farah Cook</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1958653918" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3309413977928619854">Beautiful book that doesn&apos;t focus on the concept of happiness as such but rather the measures to get there. Happiness is not a place you arrive to, and it stays for life. It&apos;s something we must actively seek all the time as we go through changes. This book is very philosophical so don&apos;t buy it if you think it gives you a formula for happiness.</span>
  <span id="freeText3309413977928619854" style="display:none">Beautiful book that doesn't focus on the concept of happiness as such but rather the measures to get there. Happiness is not a place you arrive to, and it stays for life. It's something we must actively seek all the time as we go through changes. This book is very philosophical so don't buy it if you think it gives you a formula for happiness.</span>
